---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="CUFS" description="Cambridge University Freemasons Society — affiliated with Isaac Newton University Lodge No. 859.">

  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Cambridge University Freemasons Society</h1>
    <p>CUFS — bringing Freemasonry to the University of Cambridge</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content-section">

    <div class="cufs-intro">
      <p>
        The Cambridge University Freemasons Society (CUFS) is the student society affiliated
        with Isaac Newton University Lodge No. 859. It provides a welcoming environment for
        current students and members of the University to learn more about Freemasonry, meet
        like-minded people, and take their first steps into the Craft.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="holding-block">
      <h2>About CUFS</h2>
      <p>
        Further information about the society, its events, and how to get involved will be
        published here shortly. In the meantime, please visit our Cambridge SU page or follow
        us on Instagram (<strong>@cu_freemasonry_society</strong>) for the latest updates.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="holding-block">
      <h2>Interested in Joining?</h2>
      <p>
        Whether you are a student curious about Freemasonry or an existing Mason new to
        Cambridge, CUFS is the perfect starting point. Details of upcoming events and how
        to register your interest will be added here in due course.
      </p>
      <p>
        You may also wish to explore the
        <a href="/links" class="inline-link">UGLE Universities Scheme</a>,
        which supports students joining Freemasonry at universities across England and Wales.
      </p>
    </div>

    <a href="https://www.cambridgesu.co.uk/organisation/23948/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cufs-link-card">
      <div class="cufs-link-text">
        <span class="cufs-link-title">CUFS on Cambridge SU</span>
        <span class="cufs-link-desc">Visit our official Cambridge Students' Union page to find out more and join the society.</span>
        <span class="cufs-link-url">cambridgesu.co.uk/organisation/23948</span>
      </div>
      <span class="cufs-link-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&#8599;</span>
    </a>

  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .cufs-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--cambridge-blue);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }

  .holding-block {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid #e0ddd5;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .holding-block h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--navy);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .holding-block p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .inline-link {
    color: var(--cambridge-dark);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .inline-link:hover { color: var(--navy); }

  .cufs-link-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid #e0ddd5;
    border-radius: 6px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .cufs-link-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    border-color: var(--cambridge-dark);
  }

  .cufs-link-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  .cufs-link-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--navy);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .cufs-link-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .cufs-link-url {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--cambridge-dark);
  }

  .cufs-link-arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--cambridge-dark);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .cufs-link-card:hover .cufs-link-arrow { transform: translate(2px, -2px); }
</style>
